        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2119670807" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16102716268986880232">The book’s unique cover gives you a strong hint about the forces that work inside, and that’s what attracted me to it in the first place.. Then I started to read the book and simply couldn’t stop. Every character has a unique story, some have secrets…and the author does an amazing job pulling you into the world of the young priest who uncovers secret after secret. It’s a story of good against evil written in the most fascinating way and if you enjoy a good suspense thriller , you should read it.</span>
  <span id="freeText16102716268986880232" style="display:none">The book’s unique cover gives you a strong hint about the forces that work inside, and that’s what attracted me to it in the first place.. Then I started to read the book and simply couldn’t stop. Every character has a unique story, some have secrets…and the author does an amazing job pulling you into the world of the young priest who uncovers secret after secret. It’s a story of good against evil written in the most fascinating way and if you enjoy a good suspense thriller , you should read it. Just don’t plan anything else while you read it because once you start you won’t be able to stop. </span>
