        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1790975334" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18135509088204734919">Really enjoyed this book. Starts slow but hits you hard soon after with gripping suspense and great characters, uniquely set in Dublin, Ireland, without resorting to tired stereotypes. Gory at times, but the action and dialogue - particularly the short monologue type discussion between Daniel and Jack later in the later chapters - are fresh, intense and holds your attention. Great book for a club to discuss as it explores human need and relationships. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


